mail.body:
You are leading a security audit and hardening pipeline. Your first task (scan) is ready on the task board.

Target: ${REPO_PATH:-/home/shared/inputs/repo}
Scope: ${SCAN_SCOPE:-full}

Run a comprehensive security scan of the codebase. Check for OWASP Top 10, hardcoded secrets, injection risks, auth issues, and dependency vulnerabilities. Write findings with severity ratings to /home/shared/scan-results.md.

Run: task.sh ready --owner $(whoami)
